1. *Izgubljeni* novčanik je pronađen u parku. (The *lost* wallet was found in the park.)
2. Njegova *izgubljena* torba je pronađena na autobuskoj stanici. (His *lost* bag was found at the bus station.)
3. Moramo pronaći način da ne budemo *izgubljeni* u ovom velikom gradu. (We need to find a way not to get *lost* in this big city.)
4. Nakon duge šetnje, osećali su se *izgubljeno* u šumi. (After a long walk, they felt *lost* in the forest.)
5. Mnogi ljudi su *izgubljeni* u životu i ne znaju kojim putem da idu. (Many people are *lost* in life and don't know which way to go.)